TRIP COMMENTS: with Sally Nowell and Richard Thaxton. Birds recorded during a full day in the upper part of the park, from the São Roque entrance as far as the Casca d'Anta, and then over to Cachoeira do Rolinho, before returning the way we came. Weather a mix of sun and clouds, afternoon largely overcast, with visible showers scattered around the area (though we never hit any of them, in fact they seemed to be mostly restricted to the edges of the plateau).
SPECIES COMMENTS: 1 heard near where the first transmission lines cross the road inside the park
